comment: McCollum (POR) and Bazemore (ATL) make incidental contact with one another.
Crabbe (POR) makes contact to the body of Teague (ATL) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Bazemore (ATL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends McCollum's (POR) shot attempt.
Crabbe (POR) makes incidental contact with Horford (ATL) after he releases the pass.

After communicating with the Replay Center, there was conclusive video evidence that showed that Korver (ATL) was the last player to touch the ball prior to it going OOB. The ruling on the court was overturned and Portland was awarded possession.
Horford (ATL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends McCollum's (POR) drive and shot attempt.

After communicating with the Replay Center, there was conclusive video evidence that showed that Lillard (POR) was the last player to touch the ball prior to it going OOB. The ruling on the court was overturned and Atlanta was awarded possession.
Crabbe (POR) commits a take foul on Korver (ATL).
Plumlee (POR) commits a take foul on Bazemore (ATL).
Leonard (POR) dislodges Sefolosha (ATL) affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Leonard (POR) commits a take foul on Bazemore (ATL).
Teague (ATL) makes incidental contact with Lillard (POR) that does not affect his driving layup attempt.
Millsap (ATL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Leonard's (POR) tip shot attempt.
